{"tid":1072701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"班商家報應終於嚟啦","createTime":"2019-03-22T07:33:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-26T10:35:40.000Z","uid":1988,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2256b2e668afa3643165538da1a7ea6806828874","tid":1072701,"uid":1988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T07:33:08.000Z","msg":"中國宜家要減稅刺激經濟<br />\n中共又拒絕放水俾地方政府出糧<br />\n李克強開到口要地方政府自己諗點佢<br />\n如果巴打們有係強國行過街<br />\n就會留意到依家強國街邊除左一貫嘅民主愛國呢d ff口號之外<br />\n仲多左好多反黑除惡banner<br />\n<br />\n反黑 其實就即係抄家<br />\n地方政府會唔妥你 就會屈你犯法然後將你資產充公<br />\n呢d嘢其實上年十月左右已經比比皆是<br />\n但當時主要喺針對中國嘅民企<br />\n結果打左一排d 民企頂唔順發爛渣告御狀<br />\n所以就有左單 小習習視察民企 民企老闆訴苦 嘅事<br />\n<br />\n而家李克強開埋口 唔準搞民企<br />\n台資又搞唔郁嘅情況下<br />\n反黑嘅對象就淨返香港人<br />\n<br />\n所以d 商家佬今日仲講咩豁免商業罪行<br />\n豁免？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人地就係要搞鳩你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae926f68ab9bf4ab326f3e35943bd72ac7966501","tid":1072701,"uid":59775,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T07:35:02.000Z","msg":"除咗恭喜我都唔知講乜好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91e155a2a2364abb7dadbee16f8621b7e94adcc4","tid":1072701,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T09:07:33.000Z","msg":"興奮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"018165fe523c1abe4f989013325c41d2e0aae480","tid":1072701,"uid":1988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T12:24:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4118d6621d67bc8b50735c83d2be946a20cc5c5","tid":1072701,"uid":1988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T10:35:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />林鄭又出馬"}]}